1. Block structure PL/SQL:
	BEGIN statement; END;
	Equivalent C/C++/Java/C# block:
	{ statement; 
		{ statement; }; } /* is a statement within a statementst

Mutable variable = reference to the variable
Immutable variable = copy of the value

Anything compared with NULL in an and statement is false

